    "question_id" : 6020719,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This exception is thrown if the underlying method(method called using Reflection) throws an exception.</p>\n\n<p>So if the method, that has been invoked by reflection API, throws an exception (as for example runtime exception), the reflection API will wrap the exception into an InvocationTargetException.</p>\n"
