    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This will print the exact line of code in the specific method, which when invoked, raised the exception:</p>\n\n<pre><code>try {\n\n    // try code\n    ..\n    m.invoke(testObject);\n    ..\n\n} catch (InvocationTargetException e) {\n\n    // Answer:\n    e.getCause().printStackTrace();\n} catch (Exception e) {\n\n    // generic exception handling\n    e.printStackTrace();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
