    "body" : "<p>You can compare with the original exception Class using getCause() method like this :</p>\n\n<pre><code>try{\n  ...\n} catch(Exception e){\n   if(e.getCause().getClass().equals(AssertionError.class)){\n      // handle your exception  1\n   } else {\n      // handle the rest of the world exception \n   }\n} \n</code></pre>\n"
