    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was facing the same problem. I used e.getCause().getCause() then I found that it was because of wrong parameters I was passing. There was nullPointerException in fetching the value of one of the parameters.\nHope this will help you.</p>\n"
  }, {
